# Roadmap

## Now

- Improve trust in triage decisions
- Make follow-up clearer and more useful
- Simplify setup and onboarding
- Tighten public project story and documentation
- Keep the workflow lightweight and reliable

## Next

- Improve outcome tracking
- Tighten filtering logic
- Make reports easier to understand
- Improve usability for people beyond the original creator
- Add clearer contribution paths

## Later

- Better packaging for external users
- Community-friendly contribution flow
- Optional multi-user direction
- Broader workflow support around the job search lifecycle

## Out of scope for now

- Full ATS feature set
- Mass auto-apply
- Heavy enterprise process
- Multi-tenant SaaS platform
